{"version":1,"entries":{"tv_79460_keywords":{"at":1774726988471,"data":{"id":79460,"results":[{"name":"witch","id":616},{"name":"vampire","id":3133},{"name":"supernatural","id":6152},{"name":"werewolf","id":12564},{"name":"biting","id":15208},{"name":"spin off","id":15285},{"name":"calm","id":209673},{"name":"wonder","id":240422},{"name":"admiring","id":325761},{"name":"amused","id":325765},{"name":"joyful","id":325832}]}},"person_1207629_translations":{"at":1774726990367,"data":{"id":1207629,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Yeo Jin-goo is a South Korean actor. He began his career as a child actor, notably in the television dramas Giant, Moon Embracing the Sun, and Missing You. In 2013, he played his first big-screen leading role as the titular character in action thriller Hwa-yi. Won 2012 MBC Drama Awards: Best Child Actor for his role in \"Moon Embracing the Sun\" and \"Missing You\".","name":"Yeo Jin-goo","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"여진구","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"Yeo Jin-goo (né le 13 août 1997) est un acteur sud-coréen .  Yeo a débuté sa carrière en tant qu’acteur enfant dans le film Sad Movie (2005). Surnommé \" le petit frère de la nation \",  il joue ensuite la version la plus jeune des rôles principaux dans les films et les séries télévisées tels que A Frozen Flower (2008), Giant (2010), Moon Embracing the Sun (2012), et Tu me manque (2012). Il est connu pour jouer le personnage principal dans le thriller d'action Hwayi: A Monster Boy (2013), pour lequel il a remporté le prix du meilleur nouvel acteur aux Blue Dragon Film Awards .\n\nDepuis lors, il a joué des rôles principaux dans les films Shoot Me in the Heart (2015), The Long Way Home (2015) et Warriors of the Dawn (2017). Il a également joué dans les séries Orange Marmalade (2015), The Royal Gambler (2016), Circle (2017), Reunited Worlds (2017) et The Crowned Clown (2019).","name":"Yeo Jin-gu","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"吕珍九（韩语：여진구，1997年8月13日－），韩国演员、童星出身。2005年以电影《悲伤电影》出道。名字的含义为“九个珍宝”，不用“十”是因为剩下那一个宝贝要在生活中寻找（“九”字代表循环不息，永恒的意思）。身高177公分。\n\n昵称\t国民儿子、金菇、国民弟弟、演技天才、小九、国民演员、国民年下男、国民男友\n\n国籍\t 韩国\n\n出生\t1997年8月13日（23岁）  韩国首尔特别市冠岳区\n\n职业\t演员\n\n语言\t韩语、日语、英语\n\n教育程度\t中央大学戏剧电影学系（在学）\n\n出道日期\t2005年10月20日，​15年前\n\n出道作品\t《悲伤电影》(电影)《彩虹罗曼史》(电视剧)\n\n代表作品\t《拥抱太阳的月亮》《想你》《华颐：吞噬怪物的孩子》《成为王的男人》《德鲁纳酒店》《怪物》\n\n经纪公司\tJanus Entertainment\n\n网站\tJANUS ENT 여진구\n\n朝鲜语名称\n\n谚文\t여진구\n\n汉字\t呂珍九","name":"吕珍九","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Ё Чжин Гу","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"呂珍九（여진구，Yeo Jin Goo），韓國演員、童星出身。2005年以電影《悲傷電影》出道。名字的含義為「九個珍寶」，不用「十」是因為剩下那一個寶貝要在生活中尋找（「九」字代表迴圈不息，永恆的意思）。","name":"呂珍九","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"biography":"","name":"ยอจินกู","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"ヨ・ジング","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"呂珍九（여진구，Yeo Jin Goo），韓國演員、童星出身。2005 年以電影《真的愛你》出道。名字的含義為「九個珍寶」，不用「十」是因為剩下那一個寶貝要在生活中尋找（「九」字代表迴圈不息，永恆的意思）。","name":"呂珍九","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Йо Чжін Гу","primary":false}}]}},"tv_119122_detail_vi-VN":{"at":1774726991408,"data":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/hYfuxVs3ShpGRBHZFZdbsWedw4E.jpg","created_by":[{"id":1258586,"credit_id":"606437128d22fc0053e1d136","name":"Bentley Kyle Evans","original_name":"Bent